Description.SourceString: The “Sombre” is an escort gunship that excels at deterring air-to-naval aggression. Fitted with paired machine gun turrets and boasting a heavier frame than most vessels of comparable size, this Kraunian-made K81e emerges at a moment’s notice to defend its charge.
